Pod is generally called instance ,it is smallest thing in kubernets . It contain one or more containers on it. 

Pod can run in docker by  this command 

Docker run python app # here it is run a pod which name is python app 

Docker run helper -link app1 # it is help to the above python app 

 

Here we can deploy the pod by using this command 

Kubectl run nginx  -- image nginx 

 from above nginx is pod name and --image nginx source path whereit is located in docker hub 

If it mention at that then it will be pull from the  docker hub 

 

To get the list of the pods we should use this  command 

Kubectl get pods 
